To install PERFect package use:

library(devtools)
install_github("katiasmirn/PERFect”)

Main functions: 
PERFect_sim — simultaneous PERFect filtering algorithm 
PERFect_perm — permutation PERFect filtering algorithm

Algorithms are described in 

Smirnova, E., Huzurbazar, H., Jafari, F. “PERFect: permutation filtration of microbiome data", under review.